[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Tithe</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 3 ====
HEADWORD: Tithe
<hw>Tithe</hw>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <vmorph>[<pos>imp. & p. p.</pos>
<conjf>Tithed</conjf> <pr>(?)</pr>; <pos>p. pr. & vb. n.</pos>
<conjf>Tithing</conjf>.]</vmorph> <ety>[As.
<ets>te⟦oacute⟧<?/ian</ets>.]</ety> <def>To levy a tenth part on; to tax
to the amount of a tenth; to pay tithes on.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Ye <qex>tithe</qex> mint and rue.</q> <rj><qau>Luke xi.
42.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Tithe</ent>⟦br⟧

